Ronaldo has four children. He first became a father to a son, Cristiano Jr., born on 17 June 2010 in the United States.[506] He stated that he has full custody of the child and would not be publicly revealing the identity of the mother as per agreement with her.[507][508] In January 2015, Ronaldo announced his five-year relationship with Russian model Irina Shayk had ended.[509]
